Description:

    Step 1:
        Add this pundit helper authorize method in the methods you want to apply authorization

        authorize params, :user_access?, policy_class: UsersPolicy

    Step 2:
        Don't forget to handle Pundit::NotAuthorizedError
        You can use:

        rescue_from Pundit::NotAuthorizedError, with: :user_not_authorized
        def user_not_authorized
            flash[:alert] = "Unauthorized Access"
            redirect_to(request.referrer || root_path)
        end

Example:
    rails generate blog

    This will create:
